 \var(Y_1+\cdots+Y_n)= \var(Y_1)+\cdots+\var(Y_n) + \underbrace{2\cov(Y_1,Y_2)+\cdots}_{\binom n 2 \text{ terms}} 
 n\var + 2\binom n 2 \cov = 0. 
 \var = \frac{-2\binom n 2}{n}\cov = \frac{-\cov}{n}. 
